abstract: Stephen Holden reviews show Feminine Persuasion: Ann Hampton Callaway Celebrates Women Songwriters, featuring performance by pop singer Ann Hampton Callaway, at Feinstein's/54 Below.
lead_paragraph: Ms. Callaway performs songs from the likes of Ella Fitzgerald and Sarah Vaughan in her show “Feminine Persuasion: Ann Hampton Callaway Celebrates Women Songwriters.”

headline.main: Review: Ann Hampton Callaway Honors Her Predecessors at Feinstein’s/54 Below
headline.print_headline: Her Body Now Swings With Her Voice
